ygData.messageBody:
ok, wanted to add, you guys were all really
helpful, and sorry if i jumped on the 13 year old, was a
little pissed i couldn't get eq running, sorry about
that.<br><br>on the other hand, i just want to say...i am not in
here to hook up or anything, actually i met my
boyfriend on overquest...and we are still together, in real
live, not everquest life;) it's been over a year we've
lived together and things are swell. we met on the
Luclin server and are total soul mates...what are the
odds huh? well i better get on so i can get to level
4, woohoo!<br><br>jenn aka Catriana and my
boyfriends name is Drance (those are the main characters we
are playing now) and yes..we're on the Luclin server,
feels good to go back to the first spots we ever hung
out together..haha!!!
